screen_desc: A mobile app screen displaying various home deals under $50. The top section has a search bar and a banner with the text "Refresh your home" and "Deals under $50." Below the banner, there are three product recommendations: a laptop stand, a mattress topper, and a facial roller. Further down, there are additional deals, including a mattress topper with a 30% discount and a USB to HDMI adapter with a 15% discount. The bottom navigation bar includes icons for home, user profile, shopping cart, menu, and notifications.
